  ],
  "remarks": "Nikolai Klein is the Director of JSC MZIK (a.k.a. Kalinin Machine-Building Plant). JSC MZIK is a Russian militaryindustrial state enterprise that develops combat equipment for the S-300V anti-aircraft missile system and the BUK-M1 anti-aircraft missile system deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC MZIK is part of the Joint Stock Company Almaz-Antey air and space defence corporation, a Russian state-owned arms\nmanufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
